			<link href="/cubes/maxiv-leak/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Blinky-Leak System" />
			<updated>2023-08-08T00:00:00+02:00</updated>

			
				
				<author>
					
						<name>david-mcginnis</name>
					
					
						<email>david.mcginnis@blinky-lite.org</email>
					
					
						<uri>https://github.com/Blinky-Lite</uri>
					
				</author>
			
			<summary>The Blinky-Leak system is an large scale ultra sensitive leak detector designed for remote locations.</summary>
			<content type="html" xml:base="/cubes/maxiv-leak/">&lt;!--more--&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Each module communicates wirelessly. Each module requires a power source with a voltage of 3.7 to 5.2V and draws 1.5 mA of current on average. Each module can support two channels. The detector strip is easy to install and costs 0.5 SEK /meter. The modules have been tested successfully with detector strips over 200 meters in length.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>

			
